  m_text: "<color=green>F2</color> \tOpen/Close this Window<color=grey> - Will dump
    info in console if verbose enabled</color>\n<color=green>F3</color> \tWinLevel\n<color=green>F4</color>
    \tQuitGame\n<color=green>F5</color> \tToggleRobotoInvulnerable\n<color=yellow>LeftShift</color>
    + <color=green>F5</color> \tNOT available ATM\n<color=green>F6</color> \tRobotoAddEnergy\n<color=green>F7</color>
    \tRobotoConsumeEnergy\n<color=green>F8</color> \tToggleDebugInfo<color=grey>
    - DebugInfo</color>\n<color=green>F9</color> \tSwapDevicesForPlayers\n<color=green>F12</color>
    \tTakeScreenshot\n<color=green>R</color> \tRespawn\n<color=green>Backspace</color>
    \tResetLevel\n<color=green>P</color> \tToggleFreezeGame\n<color=yellow>LeftCtrl</color>
    + <color=green>Numpad1</color> \tDealDamage\n<color=yellow>LeftCtrl</color> +
    <color=green>Numpad2</color> \tDeal Damage to all hittables in the scene\n<color=green>PageUp</color>
    \tRespawn on Checkpoint => Next\n<color=green>PageDown</color> \tRespawn on Checkpoint
    => Previous\n<color=green>Digit0</color> \tRespawn on Checkpoint: [Element] [LevelPoint]
    Spawn\n"
